        </div>
        <div class="dp-trust-item">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
          Ships in 1–3 Days
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="dp-guarantee">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/><polyline points="9 12 11 14 15 10"/></svg>
        <span>30-day satisfaction guarantee. Not happy with it? We'll make it right.</span>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  {%- comment -%} ── BELOW FOLD: DESCRIPTION ── {%- endcomment -%}
  <div class="dp-desc-section">

    {%- comment -%} Section 01 — Statement + stat row {%- endcomment -%}
    <div class="dp-statement-section">
      <div class="dp-statement-num">01 — Why It Matters</div>
      <h2 class="dp-statement-heading">Restores What Others<br><span class="dp-statement-muted">Destroy.</span></h2>
      <p class="dp-statement-body">A towel is only as good as how you maintain it. Most detergents quietly coat microfiber over time, turning performance towels into smear rags. Polaris Microfiber Detergent strips that buildup and gives performance back.</p>
      <div class="dp-stat-row">
        <div class="dp-stat">
          <div class="dp-stat-value">16 oz</div>
          <div class="dp-stat-label">Bottle Size</div>
        </div>
        <div class="dp-stat-divider"></div>
        <div class="dp-stat">
          <div class="dp-stat-value">15–20</div>
          <div class="dp-stat-label">Washes per Bottle</div>
        </div>
        <div class="dp-stat-divider"></div>
        <div class="dp-stat">
          <div class="dp-stat-value">1–2 oz</div>
          <div class="dp-stat-label">Dose per Load</div>
        </div>
        <div class="dp-stat-divider"></div>
        <div class="dp-stat">
          <div class="dp-stat-value">Neutral pH</div>
